"to\": 7776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Definitely a different situation for Steven has been created.\", \"from\": 7778, \"to\": 7840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are very much aware that if we bring Steven out here, it will not be about sport or his performance.\", \"from\": 7841, \"to\": 7944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a time before this, at least 100 tournaments in beach volleyball, where this never came up.\", \"from\": 7945, \"to\": 8046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He never had to do anything about it.\", \"from\": 8048, \"to\": 8086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we wanted to create the environment we are used to and not make it extra-special on a stage which is even bigger for these players.\\\"\", \"from\": 8087, \"to\": 8222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian cyclist Luke Plapp was rushed to hospital after suffering a horror crash in the time trials on Sunday morning.\", \"from\": 8224, \"to\": 8345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8224, \"end\": 8234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9997174385464953, \"rank\": 0.00020121415676971468, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 8243, \"end\": 8253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Plapp\", \"score\": 0.9999944966281423, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luke Plapp\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Plapp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Plapp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old, who is making his Olympics debut, came off his bike after the 13.1km checkpoint and needed abdominal surgery, according to theDaily Mail.\", \"from\": 8347, \"to\": 8501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian Olympic Committee have stated that he is in a stable condition and is recovering with his family and the Australian team doctor in hospital.\", \"from\": 8503, \"to\": 8658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8503, \"end\": 8517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.859311830783044e-50, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}, {\"begin\": 8507, \"end\": 8535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 8623, \"end\": 8638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.9541097298602859, \"rank\": 0.030753608517097953, \"text\": \"Australian team\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles has been in artistic gymnastics action at the Olympics this morning and appears to be in superb form.\", \"from\": 8660, \"to\": 8774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8660, \"end\": 8672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But concerns have been raised over an injury scare, withThe Guardianreporting that her 'limp keeps looking worse after every landing.'\", \"from\": 8776, \"to\": 8910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's pushing through the pain barrier and will be desperate to get her hands on another Olympics medal after already winning four golds, one silver and two bronze medals in the past.\", \"from\": 8912, \"to\": 9095, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paraguayan swimmer Luana Alonso confirmed that she is retiring from the sport at the age of 20 after an \\\"emotional\\\" interview at the Olympics, in which she apologised to her country.\", \"from\": 9099, \"to\": 9281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9099, \"end\": 9109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999993024176, \"rank\": 6.975713946003833e-10, \"text\": \"Paraguayan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 9118, \"end\": 9123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"score\": 0.8124999943799553, \"rank\": 0.23076923076909422, \"text\": \"Luana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luana,_Iowa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She took toInstagramafter finishing sixth in the 100m women's butterfly, 0.24 seconds behind Georgia's Ana Nizharadze, which ensured that she narrowly missed out on qualifying for the semi-finals.\", \"from\": 9283, \"to\": 9479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9376, \"end\": 9383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\", \"score\": 0.8630332684629558, \"rank\": 0.1582747039055417, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs\"}, {\"begin\": 9390, \"end\": 9400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nizharadze\", \"score\": 0.9999998864123036, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nizharadze\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nizharadze\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nizharadze\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her statement on social media read: \\\"It's official now!\", \"from\": 9481, \"to\": 9536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am retiring from swimming, thank you all so much for the support!\", \"from\": 9537, \"to\": 9604, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sorry Paraguay, I only have to thank you!\\\"\", \"from\": 9605, \"to\": 9647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Charlotte Dujardin has been seen in new footage calling her horse a \\\"b****\\\".\", \"from\": 9649, \"to\": 9725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9649, \"end\": 9667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 39-year-old withdrew from the Olympics 2024 Equestrian dressage after she appeared in a leaked video that showed her repeatedly whipping a horse during a training session.\", \"from\": 9726, \"to\": 9901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest footage shows the veteran shouting out the words \\\"you b****\\\" to her horse as she pulls its head down with her reins.\", \"from\": 9903, \"to\": 10030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The horse had seemingly annoyed her after it had jerked its head up.\", \"from\": 10031, \"to\": 10099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The incident took place at Stoneleigh showground in Warwickshire in September 2016 and was recorded by a steward.\", \"from\": 10101, \"to\": 10214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10128, \"end\": 10138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stoneleigh_Abbey\", \"score\": 0.9999999999881766, \"rank\": 1.1555798045406097e-11, \"text\": \"Stoneleigh\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stonel